'''冰島－俄羅斯關係'''（{{lang-ru|Российско-исландские отношения}}），是指[[俄罗斯联邦|俄罗斯联邦]]和[[冰島共和國|冰島共和國]]之間的雙邊關係。俄羅斯在冰島首都[[雷克雅維克|雷克雅維克]]設有大使館，冰島亦在[[莫斯科|莫斯科]]設大使館，又在兩個俄羅斯城市[[摩爾曼斯克|摩爾曼斯克]]和[[聖彼得堡|聖彼得堡]]設[[名譽領事|名譽領事]]館。兩國在經貿方面關係密切<ref>{{cite news|first=|last=|authorlink=|coauthors=|title=Iceland seeks Russian comfort|url=http://www.mnweekly.ru/columnists/20081010/55350499.html|quote=Russia received a similar official request late on Tuesday and the country's Finance Minister Alexei Kudrin was quoted by Interfax as saying: "We will consider it. Iceland has a reputation for strict budget discipline and has a high credit rating. We're looking favorably at the request." Negotiations on the loan are supposed to start on October 14.|work={{link-en|莫斯科新聞|The Moscow News}}|date=|accessdate=2009-06-26|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090531021947/http://www.mnweekly.ru/columnists/20081010/55350499.html|archivedate=2009-05-31}}</ref>。

== 歷史 ==
[[蘇聯|蘇聯]]和冰島於1943年10月4日建交<ref name=rus/><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.iceland.org/ru/english/the-embassy/bilateral-relations/ |title=Bilateral Relations |accessdate=2009-06-26 |quote=Diplomatic relations were established between Iceland and Soviet Union 1943 and in the following year Embassies were opened in Reykjavík and Moscow respectively. |publisher=[[冰岛政府|冰岛政府]] |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081120102818/http://www.iceland.org./ru/english/the-embassy/bilateral-relations/ |archivedate=2008-11-20 }}</ref>；1955年12月，兩國升格為大使級關係。自1975年至1991年，冰島在蘇聯設有貿易代表處；由1991至1995年，俄羅斯联邦於冰島設有貿易代表處<ref name=rus>{{cite web |url=http://www.iceland.mid.ru/ |title=Russian embassy in Reykjavík |accessdate=2009-06-26 |quote= |publisher=[[俄罗斯政府|俄罗斯政府]] |archive-date=2009-07-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090719001302/http://www.iceland.mid.ru/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。1997年，歷史上第一本《[[俄語|俄語]]－[[冰島語|冰島語]]詞典》出版<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-21024440.html |title=Russnesk-islensk ordabok. |accessdate=2009-06-26 |language=ru }}{{Dead link|date=2019年4月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。2002年4月18日至24日，[[冰島總統|冰島總統]][[格里姆松|格里姆松]]赴俄羅斯外訪，訪問了俄羅斯城市[[聖彼得堡|聖彼得堡]]、[[莫斯科|莫斯科]]、[[諾夫哥羅德|諾夫哥羅德]]和[[薩列哈爾德|薩列哈爾德]]<ref name=rus/><ref>{{cite news |first= |last= |authorlink= |coauthors= |title=Iceland leader arrives in Moscow |url=http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=NewsLibrary&p_multi=BBAB&d_place=BBAB&p_theme=newslibrary2&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0F978350240AD391&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM |quote=President of Iceland Olafur Grimsson arrived in Moscow on Thursday [18 April] on the first state visit in the history of the two countries' relations. At the airport, Grimsson was greeted by head of the Russian Fisheries Committee Yevgeniy Nazdratenko.The Russian Foreign Ministry told Interfax that relations between Moscow and Reykjavik "are on the rise and are developing rapidly".Upcoming Russian-Icelandic talks are expected ... |work=[[Interfax|Interfax]] at the [[BBC|BBC]] |date=April 18, 2002 |accessdate=2009-06-26 |archive-date=2012-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121019173806/http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=NewsLibrary&p_multi=BBAB&d_place=BBAB&p_theme=newslibrary2&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0F978350240AD391&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2008年，冰岛的傳統西方盟友拒絕提供財政援助，拯救該國面臨崩潰的[[銀行體系|銀行體系]]，因此[[冰岛總理|冰岛總理]][[蓋爾·哈爾德|蓋爾·哈爾德]]派出代表團，向俄國請求提供30億[[英鎊|英鎊]]（約40億[[歐元|歐元]]）的援助<ref name=tel>{{cite news |first=Rowena |last=Mason |authorlink= |coauthors= |title=Iceland nationalises bank and seeks Russian loan |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/newsbysector/banksandfinance/3154116/Financial-crisis-Iceland-nationalises-bank-and-seeks-Russian-loan.html |quote=Prime Minister Geir Haarde rushed emergency measures through the Nordic nation's parliament to nationalise Landsbanki and give the country's largest bank, Kaupthing, a £400 million loan to bolster its balance sheet. |work=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]] |date=2008-10-07 |accessdate=2009-06-26 |location=London |archive-date=2009-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090126192711/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/newsbysector/banksandfinance/3154116/Financial-crisis-Iceland-nationalises-bank-and-seeks-Russian-loan.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>；後來因應冰島成功向[[國際貨幣基金組織|國際貨幣基金組織]]及丹麥、挪威等北歐國家中央銀行借得大筆貸款，遂將與俄罗斯協商的貸款額減至5億美元，但俄羅斯最終在於2009年10月14日宣布拒絕貸款<ref name=tish>{{cite news |first= |last= |authorlink= |coauthors= |title=Russia refuses $500 million loan to Iceland |url=http://en.rian.ru/business/20091014/156468945.html |quote=Russia's government has refused to grant a $500 million loan to Iceland. Iceland originally asked Russia for a 4 billion euro ($5.8 billion) loan, but after it received most of the sum from Scandinavian countries and the IMF, the sum of the requested loan went down to $500 million. |work=[[RIA_Novosti|RIA Novosti]] |date=2009-10-14 |accessdate=2011-10-14 |location=Moscow |archive-date=2013-07-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130722003744/http://en.rian.ru/business/20091014/156468945.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2022年2月俄羅斯入侵烏克蘭後，[[冰岛总理|冰岛总理]][[卡特琳·雅各布斯多蒂爾|卡特琳·雅各布斯多蒂爾]]谴责了俄罗斯的入侵行为，<ref>{{cite web |date=24 February 2022 |title=Russians In Iceland & Icelandic Government Condemn Invasion Of Ukraine, Protests Planned |url=https://grapevine.is/news/2022/02/24/russians-in-iceland-icelandic-government-condemn-invasion-of-ukraine-protests-planned/ |access-date=2022-02-24 |website=The Reykjavik Grapevine |archive-date=2022-02-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220224233326/https://grapevine.is/news/2022/02/24/russians-in-iceland-icelandic-government-condemn-invasion-of-ukraine-protests-planned/ }}</ref>并跟隨歐美一同[[俄烏戰爭期間的國際制裁|對俄國進行制裁]]。同年3月7日，俄羅斯聯邦政府通過對其採取[[不友好國家名單|「不友善舉動」的國家與地區名單]]，[[冰岛|冰岛]]也被列入{{noteTag|[[美国|美国]]、[[欧洲联盟成员国|歐盟會員國]]、[[英国|英国]]、[[日本|日本]]、[[加拿大|加拿大]]、[[挪威|挪威]]、[[新加坡|新加坡]]、[[大韩民国|韓國]]、[[瑞士|瑞士]]、[[乌克兰|乌克兰]]、[[蒙特內哥羅|蒙特內哥羅]]、[[阿尔巴尼亚|阿尔巴尼亚]]、[[安道尔|安道尔]]、[[冰岛|冰岛]]、[[列支敦斯登|列支敦斯登]]、[[摩纳哥|摩纳哥]]、[[圣马力诺|圣马力诺]]、[[北馬其頓|北馬其頓]]、[[澳大利亚|澳洲]]、[[密克罗尼西亚联邦|密克羅尼西亞]]、[[新西兰|新西兰]]，[[中華民國|臺灣]]。}}。<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.storm.mg/article/4228158 |author = 中央社 |date = 2022年3月7日 |title = 俄羅斯「不友善」國家與地區名單 台灣也上榜 |publisher = [[風傳媒|風傳媒]]}}</ref>

== 經貿關係 ==
{{see also|冰岛经济|俄罗斯经济}}
2003年，俄羅斯和冰島兩國之間的雙邊貿易總額為8970萬美元，其中冰島到俄羅斯的出口總額為380萬美元，俄羅斯到冰島的出口總額為7590萬美元。俄羅斯是冰島第九大出口國。俄羅斯出口到冰島的產品包括[[石油|石油]]產品和[[鋁|鋁]]，而冰島出口到俄羅斯的產品則包括[[輪船|輪船]]、[[海產|海產]]、[[紡織品|紡織品]]和[[服裝|服裝]]、[[化肥|化肥]]以及[[工業|工業]]設備<ref name=rus/>。

